Date: Sat, 21 Feb 2026 16:47:06 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Add OpenClaw integration endpoints

- POST /api/openclaw/message: receive messages from OpenClaw, broadcast to WS clients
- GET /api/openclaw/conversations: list available conversations
- GET /api/openclaw/messages/:id: get recent messages for a conversation
- POST /api/openclaw/config: runtime config (placeholder)
- Add forwardToOpenClaw() helper to send messages to OpenClaw webhook
- Auto-forward chat messages to OpenClaw when OPENCLAW_WEBHOOK_URL is set
- Add getConversations() helper to db.ts

Configure via env:
- OPENCLAW_WEBHOOK_URL: webhook URL to forward messages to
- OPENCLAW_ENABLED: set to 'false' to disable (enabled by default)
